# LogShadowTrack - Hidden Signal Log Analyzer

LogShadowTrack highlights background log events that repeat with low frequency but carry strong diagnostic value.

## Features
- Shadow pattern clustering  
- Long-term frequency mapping  
- CLI export tools

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/LogShadowTrack.git
cd LogShadowTrack
python analyze.py
